-- U.K. Pound Declines Versus Dollar to Trade 0.5 Percent Weaker at $1.5858
-- B y   L u k a n y o   M n y a n d a
-- 2011-01-28T07:36:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-28/u-k-pound-declines-versus-dollar-to-trade-0-5-percent-weaker-at-1-5858.html
The U.K. pound declined against the
dollar, headed for its first weekly loss in three, to trade 0.5
percent weaker at $1.5858 as of 7.31 a.m. in  London .  Sterling fell for a second day against the euro,
depreciating by 0.2 percent to 86.38 pence.  To contact the reporter on this story:
